file.name: swagger-bare-bones-two-security-schemes.yml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Bakery
  license:
    name: MIT
components:
  securitySchemes:
    BearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
    ApiKey:
      type: apiKey
      in: header
      name: X-API-Key
